ribute.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"930\" height=\"435\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-1.jpg\" alt=\"Feature Image\" class=\"wp-image-2058\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-1.jpg 930w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-1-300x140.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-1-768x359.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-1-150x70.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After that, you have to add this attribute for the variation product.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"930\" height=\"441\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-2.jpg\" alt=\"Feature Image\" class=\"wp-image-2059\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-2.jpg 930w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-2-300x142.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-2-768x364.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-2-150x71.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Thus, you can get the result like this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"930\" height=\"625\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/unit-3.jpg\" alt=\"Feature Image\"